Class Expense

java.lang.Object
  apps.linear.Expense
Direct Known Subclasses:
DateExpense, ItemDateExpense, ItemExpense
public class Expense
extends java.lang.Object

This class encapsulates an expense consisting of a date (yyyy/mm/dd), an amount spent, and an item on which the amount was spent.

Author:
Sesh Venugopal
